1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,250
=Episode 31=

3
00:00:55,725 --> 00:00:56,640
Does it taste good?

4
00:00:56,737 --> 00:00:57,439
Here.

5
00:00:57,500 --> 00:00:59,399
I'll get you another bowl
to boost your energy.

6
00:00:59,399 --> 00:01:00,399
It's okay, Mom.

7
00:01:00,587 --> 00:01:02,119
I really can't finish a third bowl.

8
00:01:03,475 --> 00:01:03,954
Mr. Ye,

9
00:01:04,175 --> 00:01:04,815
the car is here.

10
00:01:05,975 --> 00:01:07,119
- Everything okay?
- Yeah.

11
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:08,799
People from Yanjing have arrived.

12
00:01:08,799 --> 00:01:10,190
There won't be any problems this time.

13
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:11,359
Mrs. Xiao,

14
00:01:11,675 --> 00:01:13,640
I'll wait for you and Mr. Xiao
at the door.

15
00:01:14,850 --> 00:01:15,462
Alright.

16
00:01:19,625 --> 00:01:20,815
Everything is packed.

17
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:21,920
Goodness.

18
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,390
I've packed everything we might need.

19
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:26,680
Now that we're really leaving,

20
00:01:27,387 --> 00:01:29,599
I can't help but feel a little uneasy.

21
00:01:30,650 --> 00:01:32,668
But there's nothing we can do here.

22
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,159
Dad,

23
00:01:36,879 --> 00:01:37,439
Mom,

24
00:01:38,599 --> 00:01:40,000
you don't need to worry about us.

25
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:42,079
Ye Chen and I will be fine.

26
00:01:43,510 --> 00:01:45,519
Besides, you two
haven't traveled in a long time.

27
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:46,920
Take this chance

28
00:01:47,075 --> 00:01:48,337
to go out and enjoy yourselves.

29
00:01:50,462 --> 00:01:53,000
I understand what you two are doing.

30
00:01:53,700 --> 00:01:55,326
You're doing this for us.

31
00:01:55,925 --> 00:01:57,910
Whatever you decide
must be the right choice.

32
00:01:58,250 --> 00:01:59,591
I only have one request.

33
00:01:59,887 --> 00:02:00,920
Eat well.

34
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,290
Take good care of your health.

35
00:02:06,319 --> 00:02:07,200
Don't worry, Mom.

36
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,239
Alright.

37
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:09,400
I've got to go now.

38
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:14,639
Okay.

39
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:15,960
Got it.

40
00:02:20,225 --> 00:02:21,457
Mom and Dad have landed safely.

41
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,360
That's good.

42
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,360
Next,

43
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:27,080
we can focus on dealing with Wu Donghai.

44
00:02:27,175 --> 00:02:27,719
Yeah.

45
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,400
Honey,

46
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,159
I dragged you all into this.

47
00:02:38,380 --> 00:02:40,120
Every time I think about
how you were in danger...

48
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,479
Why are you bringing this up again?

49
00:02:42,639 --> 00:02:45,319
We've already been
through life and death together.

50
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,159
Why do you keep going on about it?

51
00:02:48,610 --> 00:02:49,680
You're underestimating me.

52
00:02:50,439 --> 00:02:51,400
I would never do that.

53
00:02:51,812 --> 00:02:54,130
If you hadn't helped me that day,

54
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,439
I'd probably

55
00:02:55,575 --> 00:02:57,410
be dead by now.

56
00:03:00,512 --> 00:03:01,639
Tell me then.

57
00:03:01,837 --> 00:03:03,199
What's your plan next?

58
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:07,039
My plan is

59
00:03:07,039 --> 00:03:09,199
to hold my wife
and get a good night's sleep.

60
00:03:10,262 --> 00:03:12,439
At a time like this, can you be serious?

61
00:03:12,439 --> 00:03:13,700
When have I ever been serious?

62
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:17,080
It's mainly because I feel bad
for my wife.

63
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:19,180
You haven't had a proper rest
these past few days.

64
00:03:20,562 --> 00:03:24,159
As your husband, it really pains me.

65
00:03:26,337 --> 00:03:27,520
So are you sleeping or not?

66
00:03:27,919 --> 00:03:29,639
Wasn't I just about to?

67
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:31,520
You're still injured.

68
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,919
What are you trying to do?

69
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:35,199
At a time like this,
who cares about injuries?

70
00:03:35,860 --> 00:03:36,599
Come here, honey.

71
00:03:37,039 --> 00:03:38,190
Don't hold back because of me.

72
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:42,360
Honey.

73
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:44,280
Honey...

74
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,680
I have something to tell you.

75
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:55,520
Honey, I'm still a little worried.

76
00:03:55,850 --> 00:03:56,918
How about we don't go?

77
00:03:59,262 --> 00:04:01,112
I'm just going out
to buy some groceries.

78
00:04:02,212 --> 00:04:03,800
Aoxue will be with me.

79
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:07,680
The most important thing right now
is that you stay safe.

80
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:08,319
I'll be fine.

81
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:09,719
Don't worry.

82
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:13,880
I'm heading out.

83
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,639
Once you get Ye Chen's
neural gene mutation data,

84
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:23,800
send it to me immediately.

85
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:24,600
Understood.

86
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:32,000
Grandpa, we can't just sit around
waiting anymore.

87
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,360
We must help Ye Chen
bring down the Wu family.

88
00:04:34,837 --> 00:04:36,360
I've wronged the Ye family.

89
00:04:36,612 --> 00:04:37,919
If I can help Ye Chen,

90
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,519
it will count as making amends.

91
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,720
Madam,

92
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,680
you're busy all day.

93
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,390
It looks more tiring
than one of my fights.

94
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:53,600
Every job has its own hardships.

95
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,120
No.

96
00:04:55,375 --> 00:04:56,775
I think you have it even tougher.

97
00:04:56,850 --> 00:04:58,900
(Xiao Weiwei)

98
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:07,199
Churan,

99
00:05:07,199 --> 00:05:09,360
please save me.

100
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:09,990
What happened?

101
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:12,160
Our family ran out of money,

102
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,600
so I took a job at the hot spring.

103
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,600
A guest just now accused me

104
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,680
of breaking his jade bracelet.

105
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,040
But I didn't even touch it.

106
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,600
They demanded compensation.

107
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,890
How could I possibly
have that kind of money?

108
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,079
And they...

109
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:25,920
They...

110
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,720
Enough nonsense!

111
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,360
Weiwei!

112
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,050
Listen carefully.

113
00:05:28,537 --> 00:05:29,400
Bring half a million

114
00:05:29,762 --> 00:05:30,439
to redeem her.

115
00:05:30,537 --> 00:05:32,160
Not a cent less.

116
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,120
If you don't,

117
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:36,000
I'll sell her to settle it.

118
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:37,519
Come to Guanlan Hot Spring.

119
00:05:37,912 --> 00:05:38,639
Hurry up.

120
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:39,759
If you're late,

121
00:05:40,399 --> 00:05:41,639
you'll never see her again.

122
00:05:41,639 --> 00:05:43,480
Churan, please come save me!

123
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,519
Madam,

124
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:51,839
why don't we

125
00:05:52,439 --> 00:05:54,199
ask Master first?

126
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,920
Your master is still recovering.

127
00:05:56,620 --> 00:05:57,600
It's such a small matter.

128
00:05:58,199 --> 00:05:59,160
Let's not trouble him.

129
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:07,680
Madam.

130
00:06:07,959 --> 00:06:08,600
You go ahead.

131
00:06:09,100 --> 00:06:09,959
I'll check over there.

132
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:11,199
Alright.

133
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,319
You actually came.

134
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:31,000
Mrs. Ye,

135
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:32,319
what a pleasure.

136
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:35,560
Get inside!

137
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,240
Hurry!

138
00:06:38,319 --> 00:06:39,560
Let go of her!

139
00:06:41,079 --> 00:06:43,120
Tell Ye Chen to wait for my call!

140
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:47,759
Let go of her!

141
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,160
Stop right there!

142
00:06:57,090 --> 00:06:58,199
What are you staring at?

143
00:06:59,380 --> 00:06:59,920
That's right.

144
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:01,279
I lied to you.

145
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,879
So what?

146
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,279
You were just too stupid.

147
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:06,800
Do you know

148
00:07:07,325 --> 00:07:08,872
how much I hate you?

149
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:11,079
Since we were kids,
I've been smarter than you.

150
00:07:11,079 --> 00:07:11,925
And prettier than you.

151
00:07:12,079 --> 00:07:13,879
Why do you get
to live better than me now?

152
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,439
Begging you to save me?

153
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:18,040
I wish you'd just die already!

154
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,240
Xiao Weiwei.

155
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:19,639
You!

156
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,160
You're truly pathetic.

157
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:25,279
The one who's pathetic now

158
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,560
seems to be you.

159
00:07:27,750 --> 00:07:28,839
Stay calm even in danger.

160
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:31,360
Mrs. Ye, you truly have nerves of steel.

161
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:33,519
Ye Chen will come save me.

162
00:07:34,175 --> 00:07:36,381
No matter what you're planning,
you won't succeed.

163
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,879
Still counting on that useless man?

164
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:42,240
What makes him think
he can compare with Mr. Wu?

165
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:43,879
Xiao Weiwei,

166
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,920
do you really think
you've latched onto Wu Xin?

167
00:07:46,250 --> 00:07:48,439
He's just using you
as a tool to hurt others.

168
00:07:48,587 --> 00:07:49,399
Believe it or not,

169
00:07:49,879 --> 00:07:51,759
he'll dump you the moment he's done.

170
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:53,370
How is that possible?

171
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,600
Mr. Wu has promised me.

172
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,399
He would help the Xiao family rise again.

173
00:07:58,839 --> 00:08:00,519
He will treat me well.

174
00:08:00,879 --> 00:08:02,160
Am I right, Mr. Wu?

175
00:08:04,079 --> 00:08:05,639
You believe everything I say?

176
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:07,959
Get out.

177
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:08,759
Get out!

178
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:11,959
Stop the car!

179
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:26,800
Hello, Mr. Ye.

180
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,319
Looks like we're meeting again.

181
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,000
There's a car waiting outside.

182
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,399
Come alone,

183
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,639
or she dies.

184
00:08:33,160 --> 00:08:35,212
If you call the police, she dies too.

185
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:36,200
Churan, don't be afraid.

186
00:08:37,040 --> 00:08:37,625
I'm coming.

187
00:08:51,679 --> 00:08:52,080
Churan?

188
00:08:52,559 --> 00:08:53,960
Churan! Churan!

189
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:54,440
Churan!

190
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:56,120
It's okay.

191
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:56,759
I'm here.

192
00:08:57,700 --> 00:08:58,370
You'll be fine.

193
00:08:58,639 --> 00:09:00,639
Still talking tough
when you're about to die?

194
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:01,840
Mr. Duan,

195
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:04,960
let's settle the real business first.

196
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:06,679
Wu Xin,

197
00:09:07,039 --> 00:09:09,200
tell me, what do you want from me?

198
00:09:09,725 --> 00:09:10,440
Dr. Bai,

199
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,650
please introduce the fine device

200
00:09:12,650 --> 00:09:13,931
in your hand to Mr. Ye.

201
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,729
It's a portable gene sequencer.

202
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,520
All it needs is a bottle of your blood.

203
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:18,360
Within an hour,

204
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,120
it can map your entire gene sequence.

205
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,160
I thought it would be something serious.

206
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:22,720
Fine.

207
00:09:24,530 --> 00:09:25,925
But you have to release her first.

208
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:35,395
Are you trying to negotiate with me?

209
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:37,799
Are you?

210
00:09:38,987 --> 00:09:39,639
Wu Xin!

211
00:09:40,210 --> 00:09:41,480
I've looked into your background.

212
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:43,200
You're nothing but sc*m!

213
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,080
Tell me about it.

214
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,720
In 2018,

215
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,879
you drugged
and assaulted a college girl.

216
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,440
She jumped off a building,

217
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,500
and her family was ruined.

218
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:55,600
In 2020,

219
00:09:56,279 --> 00:09:57,759
you drove drunk and killed an old man.

220
00:09:58,159 --> 00:10:00,486
In 2023, there was a brutal assault

221
00:10:00,486 --> 00:10:02,437
at the Donghai Group construction site.

222
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:03,950
More than a dozen people were killed.

223
00:10:04,300 --> 00:10:05,600
Relying on your money and power,

224
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:08,080
you threatened and bribed your way
out of punishment.

225
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,350
Wu Xin, let me tell you this.

226
00:10:11,039 --> 00:10:13,039
I now have more than enough evidence.

227
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,879
I can send you to prison anytime.

228
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,519
Mr. Tang, you have to be careful.

229
00:10:30,937 --> 00:10:31,576
Stop there.

230
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:32,960
Who are you?

231
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:35,080
Tang Sihai.

232
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,799
Let's end this.

233
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:40,159
End this?

234
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:44,000
More like you surrendering.

235
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:45,919
Surrender

236
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,799
comes with a price.

237
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,679
What are you offering me?

238
00:10:54,039 --> 00:10:55,550
I won't go after Changying and his wife

239
00:10:56,039 --> 00:10:57,399
for their deaths.

240
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,490
As for the formula,

241
00:10:58,850 --> 00:11:00,960
Ye Chen can decrypt it for you.

242
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,919
You can take it.

243
00:11:01,919 --> 00:11:03,279
But I have one condition.

244
00:11:04,050 --> 00:11:06,080
You must not harm Ye Chen
or Xiao Churan.

245
00:11:08,725 --> 00:11:09,440
Anything else?

246
00:11:09,762 --> 00:11:11,279
You can have Dihao Group too.

247
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:18,799
That's it?

248
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:20,519
I thought it would be something big.

249
00:11:21,737 --> 00:11:24,137
Mr. Ye, you really disappoint me.

250
00:11:24,425 --> 00:11:26,039
This is no fun at all.

251
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:27,440
I,

252
00:11:27,879 --> 00:11:28,679
Wu Xin,

253
00:11:29,250 --> 00:11:30,515
is the son of Wu Donghai.

254
00:11:31,150 --> 00:11:32,919
What can you possibly do to me?

255
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,559
But right now, I can touch your woman

256
00:11:38,087 --> 00:11:39,440
anytime I want.

257
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,080
Churan!

258
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,320
I'll cooperate!

259
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,200
I'll cooperate with everything!

260
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,679
I'm begging you. Please let her go!

261
00:11:56,279 --> 00:11:57,360
Churan!

262
00:11:57,370 --> 00:11:58,039
I'm begging you!

263
00:11:58,039 --> 00:11:58,759
Please let her go!

264
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,799
You should've begged earlier.

265
00:12:03,519 --> 00:12:05,600
You really don't know
how to treat a lady.

266
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,519
Dr. Bai,

267
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,080
let's begin.

268
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:09,919
Yes.

269
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:13,600
Ye Chen!

270
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:14,600
Ye Chen!

271
00:12:15,300 --> 00:12:16,100
I'll do it myself.

272
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:21,600
Ye Chen!

273
00:12:44,039 --> 00:12:45,759
You're truly loyal

274
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:47,519
to the Ye family father and son.

275
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,399
Cut the nonsense.

276
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:50,919
Do you agree or not?

277
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,039
Of course...

278
00:12:52,799 --> 00:12:53,360
not.

279
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,840
Wu Donghai!

280
00:12:55,399 --> 00:12:56,799
You've shown some sincerity.

281
00:12:57,159 --> 00:12:58,679
Too bad it's too late.

282
00:12:59,039 --> 00:13:00,559
If you dare touch Ye Chen,

283
00:13:01,159 --> 00:13:02,919
I will use all my power

284
00:13:02,919 --> 00:13:03,720
and all my time

285
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:04,879
to make your life

286
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,279
a living hell!

287
00:13:06,639 --> 00:13:07,399
Do you think

288
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,919
you still have that chance?

289
00:13:29,712 --> 00:13:32,200
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

290
00:13:32,287 --> 00:13:36,040
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

291
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:41,437
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

292
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:43,887
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

293
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:46,880
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

294
00:13:47,950 --> 00:13:50,575
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

295
00:13:50,875 --> 00:13:53,887
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

296
00:13:54,087 --> 00:13:57,137
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

297
00:13:57,250 --> 00:14:00,212
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

298
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:03,637
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

299
00:14:03,862 --> 00:14:07,612
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

300
00:14:07,612 --> 00:14:10,475
♪I belong to no one♪

301
00:14:10,537 --> 00:14:13,987
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

302
00:14:13,987 --> 00:14:16,662
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

303
00:14:16,662 --> 00:14:23,000
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
